as in her own bathtub.

82
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:13,950
So no splashing,

83
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,110
no signs of distress ?

84
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:16,260
No, that's what
I'm telling you.

85
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:18,500
Did you see any
shadows in the water,

86
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:20,120
maybe,

87
