No, again, she was
really far out there.

89
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:26,430
You ever see any strange
tracks by the shoreline ?

90
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,330
No, never.

91
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,220
Why ?

92
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,630
What do you think's out there ?

93
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:32,270
