was nothing down there.

114
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:27,830
That's weird, though.

115
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:29,790
That's the third
missing body this year.

116
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,920
I know.

117
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:33,270
These are people from my town.

118
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:34,860
These are people I care about.

119
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,750
I know.

120
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,090
Anyway . . .

121
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:40,930
All this.

122
