Well, the dam,
of course.

125
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,230
Of course.

126
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,350
The dam.

127
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:52,650
It's, uh...

128
00:06:54,030 --> 00:06:54,850
It sprung a leak.

129
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,000
It's falling apart,

130
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:59,240
