much of a lake.

134
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,950
There won't be much
of a town, either,

135
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,110
but as federal wildlife,

136
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:09,570
you already knew that.

137
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:11,050
Exactly.

138
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,550
Sorry, am I interrupting ?

139
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,240
I think come back later.

140
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:17,300
Gentlemen, this is my daughter.

141
