of a reasonably priced motel ?

159
00:07:58,710 --> 00:08:01,310
Lakefront motel, go around
the corner, it's two blocks up.

160
00:08:01,370 --> 00:08:02,060
Two.

161
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:03,630
Would you mind showing us ?

162
00:08:04,970 --> 00:08:06,580
You want me to
walk you two blocks ?

163
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:07,890
Not if it's any trouble.

164
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:10,260
I'm headed that way anyway.

165
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,330
I'll be back to pick up lucas at 3:00.

166
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:15,090
We'll go to the park,
okay, sweetie ?

167
00:08:18,890 --> 00:08:19,960
