168
00:08:20,980 --> 00:08:22,160
So, cute kid.

169
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,060
Thanks.

170
00:08:25,130 --> 00:08:26,540
Kids are the best, huh ?

171
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,480
There it is.

172
00:08:32,070 --> 00:08:33,510
Like I said, two blocks.

173
00:08:33,590 --> 00:08:34,330
Thanks.

174
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:37,470
Must be hard with
your sense of direction,

175
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:40,610
