that you even know.

180
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:58,200
I'm thinking.

181
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:01,000
So there's the three
drowning victims this year.

182
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:01,940
And before that ?

183
00:09:02,070 --> 00:09:04,740
Yeah, six more,

184
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,280
